tonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 18, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vel1665702657161.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vel1665702657161.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vel1665702657161.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vel1665702657161\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /tra\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Compile keyboard translation tables.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vel1665702657161__section_w2983ab1b5b1_w2984ab1b5_w2985ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vel1665702657161__p_d151505e1_d151506e1_d151507e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/tra</span> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/aft=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/bef=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/fil</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vel1665702657161__section_w2986ab1b5b3_w2987ab1b5_w2988ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1159293e82\">\n                  \n Switches\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vel1665702657161__li_d52730e1_d52731e1_d52732e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ide1665702625805.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ide1665702625805.html\" title=\"Compile objects modified after and/or before the date specified.\">/aft= or /bef=</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vel1665702657161__li_d52733e1_d52734e1_d52735e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vqk1665702657231.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vqk1665702657231.html\" title=\"Specify input file name to create and compile the keyboard translation table.\">/fil</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vel1665702657161__section_w2989ab1b5b5_w2990ab1b5_w2991ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1159293e111\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vel1665702657161__p_d151514e1_d151515e1_d151516e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>—name of the library containing the objects to compile; if omitted, all keyboard translation tables are compiled. You can use wildcard characters to specify a group of libraries.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vel1665702657161__section_w2992ab1b5b7_w2993ab1b5_w2994ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1159293e123\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vel1665702657161__d5931e20\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.exe</span>—Uniface IDE</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vel1665702657161__section_w2995ab1b5b9_w2996ab1b5_w2997ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1159293e135\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vel1665702657161__p_d151526e1_d151527e1_d151528e1\">The location of compiled translation tables is determined by the $RSO path.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfc1665702625593.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Compiling from the IDE Command Line</a><p>The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mew1705662925747.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Keyboard Translation Tables</a><p>A keyboard translation table maps a sequence of input codes received from a keyboard or database to logical function codes and characters recognized by Uniface.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hly1665702657301.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/key</a><p>Build keyboard translation tables in a character-based interface.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532982\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532982\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/tra Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 18, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /tra Compile keyboard translation tables. /tra { /aft= DateTime } { /bef= DateTime } { /fil FileName } { Library } Switches /aft= or /bef= /fil Parameters Library —name of the library containing the objects to compile; if omitted, all keyboard translation tables are compiled. You can use wildcard characters to specify a group of libraries. Use With ide.exe —Uniface IDE Description The location of compiled translation tables is determined by the $RSO path. Related Links Compiling from the IDE Command Line The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts. Keyboard Translation Tables A keyboard translation table maps a sequence of input codes received from a keyboard or database to logical function codes and characters recognized by Uniface. /key Build keyboard translation tables in a character-based interface. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}